---
title: Cajun Spiced Chicken and Chive Dressing with Mixed Potato and Cavolo Nero Mash
description: This delicious Cajun Spiced Chicken and Chive Dressing has been expertly designed by our chefs as a lighter option to help with a balanced lifestyle.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220930_R24_W45_UK_G1440-11652-4_MB_Main_low-ddf8153b.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/cajun-spiced-chicken-and-chive-dressing-63174bd86f3721b4fde339f1-3b16ec07.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/cajun-spiced-chicken-and-chive-dressing-63174bd86f3721b4fde339f1
